#

Quinoa Salad with Chickpeas and Avocado

35 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freevegetarianhealthy

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

main dish

Tags:

saladeasyhealthy

Description

A refreshing and nutritious salad packed with protein, healthy fats, and vibrant flavors.

Ingredients

  • quinoa: 1 cup
  • chickpeas (canned, drained and rinsed): 1 can (15 oz)
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • red onion: 1/4 small
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley (chopped): 1/4 cup
